title: Add ANY-FTM, lower COVER, BAND
body:
Should we add an ANY-FTM Farm?

To pay for it without diluting rewards we propose to also lower the weights of the low volume COVER-FTM and BAND-FTM pair farms which results in the following changes:

| Farm      | Weight (old) | Weight (new) | 
|-----------|--------------|------------|
| COVER-FTM | 1            | 0.4          | 
| BAND-FTM  | 1            | 0.6          | 
| ANY-FTM   | 0            | 1            |
